## How This File Works
Claude Code reads this file at the start of every conversation. It tells Claude who you are, what you're building, and what rules to follow. Do not delete or rename this file.

**Every session:**
1. Tell Claude what you want to work on today.
2. Claude reads `bounty/PROGRESS.md` to remember where you left off.
3. Build. (LaunchFlow tracking is automatic — see below.)

