## LaunchFlow Work Tracking
**Automatic.** The install prompt wired up a Claude Code hook that registers every session with LaunchFlow — you never run a "start session" command. Sessions appear on the Live Work tab at https://launchflow.msplaunchpad.com within seconds of Claude Code starting.

If LaunchFlow shows nothing for you:
1. Check `~/.launchflow/.env` has your `LAUNCHFLOW_MEMBER_NAME`, `LAUNCHFLOW_SUPABASE_URL`, and `LAUNCHFLOW_SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY`.
2. Re-run `node scripts/launchflow-setup.js` from the `level-up` repo. It's idempotent.
3. Ask Thanh.

